{
  "stem": "16345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Also, it was against the rules to drink any of that stuff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But most of us were walking around drunk most of the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 10.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was one of the youngest alcoholics around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they caught you drunk or drinking that stuff-- as a matter of fact, we had to siphon it out of the-- they had railroad cars full of that stuff.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we learned how to bleed some of it off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they caught you with any of this alcohol, or they caught you drunk, on Sundays-- which was our day off-- they had a ceremony where they hanged everybody who was caught [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] drinking.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, just as it didn't deter me from getting food any place I could, it didn't deter me from drinking much.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The main thing was don't get caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of the incidents that happened over there, another guy and I, it-- they had a narrow gauge railroad in Pionki at that factory.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And another guy and I were transporting, pushing, a cart with a bunch of cart-- with a bunch of boxes of gunpowder.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it had a brake on it that-- but the brake-- the brakes failed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew that if this thing crashed into-- if this wagon crashed into anything, and it exploded, we'd both be executed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I tried to stop it from the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He ran.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I tried to stop it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Finally, it ran over me and it-- my leg, my left, upper thigh, stopped it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was praised for it, and I was given the rest of the day off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember I got a hold of two potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
